All Classes and Interfaces

Classes
Class
Description
Branch
The Branch class creates a branch object which represents an estate agents branch in a certain area and what house sales have happened in it.
Reporting
The Reporting class creates a reporting object, which holds all the Branch objects and uses methods to get certain statistics on about all the branches.
ReportingIO
The ReportingIO class has the main method of the program and contains all the methods that deals with the IO of the program.
Sale
The Sale class creates a sale object which represents a new sale that is done by an estate agents branch.
